Could the burro have a grazing problem?

69
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:07,870
-这样会更有故事性 -无聊~~
- That would make him more...relatable.. -Boring!

70
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:09,640
这一点也不可能
It's not believable!

71
