Sometimes I throw up!

73
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:17,170
他们从此过着幸福的生活
They lived happily ever after...

74
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:19,920
不可能有比这个更让人满意的结尾了
You can't get more satisfying than that!

75
00:07:20,020 --> 00:07:21,750
一个幸福的大家庭
One big happy family!

76
00:07:22,030 --> 00:07:23,400
这是理所当然的
That's the way it supposed to be!

77
00:07:23,420 --> 00:07:25,920
那么,你的幸福家庭在哪里呢
Then, where's your big, happy family?

78
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:34,480
