79
00:07:37,630 --> 00:07:39,630
-你还好吧,哥们儿 -当然,为什么会有事
- You ok, buddy? - Sure, why not?!

80
00:07:39,620 --> 00:07:42,970
-我只是觉得你... -故事时间结束了,没有了
- I just thought you.. - Storytimes over....the end!

81
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:44,720
-大家快跑啊,想活命就快跑 -Hey~等等
- Out of the way! Run for your lives! - Hey, watch it!

82
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,040
你们这是去哪儿呢
Where's everybody going?

83
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,500
世界末日就要来了
The world's coming to an end!

84
00:07:47,980 --> 00:07:49,240
你在说什么呢
What are you talking about?

85
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:52,170
Fast Tony! 他说这个世界将被洪水淹没
Fast Tony! He says the world's going to flood!

86
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:55,400
伙计们,我手里拿着的这根小管子
Folks,I hold in my hand a device so powerful..

87
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:56,610
可以让你把空气
it can actually pull air...

88
00:07:56,610 --> 00:07:58,360
一直呼到天上去
right out of the sky!!

89
00:07:58,580 --> 00:08:00,510
过来看看吧,来看看吧
Gather round...gather round!

90
00:08:01,470 --> 00:08:03,930
打扰一下,您有鳃吗,夫人
Pardon me, do you have gills ma'am?

91
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,930
所以你不能在水里呼吸对吧
So you can't breathe under water?

92
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:08,630
我的助手可以为你示范
My assistant here will demonstrate!

93
00:08:08,910 --> 00:08:11,720
Hey~~我可以闻到海洋的味道
Hey, I can smell the ocean!

94
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,990
笨蛋,你在这做什么呢
What are you doing...?

95
00:08:12,990 --> 00:08:15,210
我不能卖它了
I can't sell that now...!!

96
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:17,510
这个是要塞进嘴里的,你个笨蛋
You suck air through your mouth you moron!!

97
00:08:18,300 --> 00:08:21,220
如果你想知道,我现在就给你讲解
If you're a pupil of mine, and I'm starting instruction...

98
00:08:21,220 --> 00:08:23,710
有了这个,不管是横渡海峡,还是 绕着小岛游一圈,都不会有问题
you'll have plenty of air for eons to come!

99
00:08:24,470 --> 00:08:26,970
当然,不要把它放到水下
Of course, don't stay buried!

100
00:08:27,730 --> 00:08:30,090
为什么你要用末日来吓唬大家
Why are you scaring everybody with this doomsday stuff?

101
00:08:31,220 --> 00:08:32,890
