I'm trying to make a living here pal..

102
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:37,210
这只是我的预言中的一部分
It's all part of my weather forecast!

103
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:40,250
五天激烈的水灾,接着就是
The 5 day outlook is calling for intense flooding, followed by..

104
00:08:40,350 --> 00:08:42,440
世界末日!
the end of the world..!!

105
00:08:43,470 --> 00:08:44,930
当薄冰碰到灼热的阳光
With a slight chance of patchy sunshine

106
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,170
接下来的那周...
..later in the week

107
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:48,610
得了吧,别听他的了
Come on! Don't listen to him..

108
00:08:48,590 --> 00:08:51,080
