Are you making an offer?

110
00:08:52,970 --> 00:08:55,480
我是说,不,我没有胡说
I mean no! I would not!

111
00:08:55,890 --> 00:08:58,130
你们没听说吗,这些冰一直在融化
Haven't you heard? The ice is melting!

112
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,400
这个地方被冰雪覆盖着
You see this ground? It's covered in ice

113
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:02,950
一千年前就是如此
A thousand years ago it was covered in ice..

114
00:09:02,950 --> 00:09:04,280
一千年以后
A thousand years from now..

115
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,850
也会如此
it will still be ice!

116
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:11,030
嘿,哥们,呃 且不去质疑你的生存本能
Say, buddy..not to cast aspersions on your survival instincts, but..

117
00:09:11,050 --> 00:09:13,720
