haven't mammoths pretty much gone extinct?

118
00:09:13,730 --> 00:09:14,810
你在说什么呢
What are you talking about?

119
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:17,480
我说得是 你应该是你们族的最后一个了
I'm talking about you being the last of your kind!

120
00:09:18,010 --> 00:09:20,930
啊!你没刷牙吧
Ahh! Your breath smells like ants!

121
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:25,390
既然你不想承认
Be as that as it may..

122
00:09:25,390 --> 00:09:27,810
那你什么时候看见过其它猛犸象呢
When's the last time you saw another mammoth?

123
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:31,580
啊! 别理他,Manny
Ah! Don't pay any attention to him Manny

124
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:33,250
猛犸象才不会灭绝
Mammoths can't go extinct..

125
00:09:33,230 --> 00:09:34,890
我们是世界上最庞大的生物
they are the biggest things on earth!

126
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:36,570
那恐龙呢?
What about the dinosaurs?

127
00:09:36,590 --> 00:09:38,260
恐龙都有怪癖
The dinosaurs got cocky!

128
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:39,830
-这样会给他们带来敌人 -快看~~
They made enemies! -Look!...

129
00:09:39,830 --> 00:09:42,330
