是大家对死者的尊敬
is respect for the dead!

146
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:24,230
得了吧,Manny! 他才没那么蠢
Come on Manny! He's not that stupid..!

147
00:10:25,350 --> 00:10:27,110
难道我以前都错了
But, I've been wrong before!

148
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:28,750
