Geronimo!!!

149
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:33,620
Hey, 看着点儿!
Hey, watch it!

150
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:42,070
我不能呼吸了
I can't breath...

151
00:10:42,990 --> 00:10:45,140
我的脾脏都要出来了!
I think I just coughed up my spleen!

152
00:10:59,970 --> 00:11:02,880
啊! Diego! 收回你的爪子,谢谢!
Ahh! Diego! Retract the claws please!

153
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,650
噢,好的,不好意思!
Oh...right...sorry!

154
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,720
如果不是我了解你,Diego..
You know, if I didn't know you better Diego..

155
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,780
我会认为你怕水,哈哈哈~~
I'd think you're afraid of the water..

156
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:11,860
好了,好了,这下我更了解你了
Ok..Ok! Good thing I know you better!

157
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,110
伙计们
Guys...!

158
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:15,620
看来Fast Tony是对的!
Fast Tony was right..!

159
00:11:16,950 --> 00:11:18,410
所有的东西都在融化
everything is melting!

160
00:11:44,180 --> 00:11:45,680
洪水就要泛滥了
It's all gonna flood...

161
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,280
快点!我们要告诉他们
Come on! We're gotta warn them.

162
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:51,320
也许我们可以快速进化成水生动物
Maybe we can rapidly evolve into water creatures.

163
00:11:51,390 --> 00:11:53,070
你真是天才, sid
That's genius, Ed...

164
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,630
叫我"乌贼"
Call me 'Squid'.

165
