Gees..this whole thing's a piece of junk!

166
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:01,030
我简直不敢相信我住在这
I can't believe I live here!

167
00:12:04,230 --> 00:12:05,810
怎么了?
What?

168
00:12:11,310 --> 00:12:12,480
这个没用
I can breathe..

169
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:15,440
我找到了它的革命性产品,我们管它叫做
I present you with this revolutionary gizmo, we call..

170
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,440
木板!!
Bark!!

171
00:12:16,450 --> 00:12:18,430
最重要的是,它可以浮起来
It's so buoyant, it actually floats!

172
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,550
我会让你看到什么东西能浮起来
I'll show you something that floats!

173
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:24,220
尽管笑吧,你们的死期快到了
Alright.... it's your funeral!

174
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:36,940
看到了吧!这正是我所说过的
You see! This is exactly what I'm talking about!

175
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:38,470
